---

<Layout title="Airbnb Photography Toronto & GTA | Professional Listing Photos" description="Professional Airbnb photography in Toronto and the Greater Toronto Area. Stunning listing photos that get more bookings at higher rates. HDR, twilight shots, and drone photography available.">
  <section class="hero hero-small">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Professional Airbnb Photography</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Stunning photos that stop scrollers and convert browsers into bookers. The single highest-ROI investment for your listing.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="trust-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="trust-grid">
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-number">23%</span>
          <span class="trust-label">Higher Rates</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-number">40%</span>
          <span class="trust-label">More Bookings</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-number">48hr</span>
          <span class="trust-label">Photo Delivery</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section intro-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <p class="intro-text">Airbnb is a visual platform. Guests scroll through dozens of listings, and you have about 2 seconds to grab their attention. Professional photos are the difference between getting clicked and getting skipped.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> 25-40 HDR-processed photos</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Professional equipment and lighting</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Staging guidance included</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Twilight and drone options</li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span> Airbnb-optimized sizing</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Book Photo Shoot</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section info-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-box highlight-box">
          <h3>Why Professional Photos Matter</h3>
          <p>According to Airbnb's own data, listings with professional photos earn up to 40% more than those with amateur shots. That's not a small improvement — it's the difference between breaking even and profitable hosting.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box tip-box">
          <h3>Pro Tip: Photo Order Matters</h3>
          <p>Your first 5 photos appear in Airbnb's preview. Lead with your best shot, then bedroom, then kitchen/living. Bathroom photos should come later. We help you arrange for maximum impact.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section comparison-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>The ROI of Professional Photos</h2>
        <p class="serif">Professional photos pay for themselves within days</p>
      </div>
      <div class="comparison-grid">
        <div class="comparison-card">
          <h4>DIY Phone Photos</h4>
          <p>Average nightly rate</p>
          <span class="result">$125</span>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-card highlight">
          <h4>Professional Photos</h4>
          <p>Average nightly rate</p>
          <span class="result">$155</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="comparison-note">That's $30/night more — or $900+/month at typical occupancy.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section packages-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Photography Packages</h2>
        <p class="serif">Options for every property type</p>
      </div>
      <div class="packages-grid">
        {packages.map(pkg => (
          <div class="package-card">
            <h3>{pkg.title}</h3>
            <p>{pkg.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section steps-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p class="serif">From booking to beautiful photos</p>
      </div>
      <div class="steps-grid">
        {steps.map(step => (
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">{step.number}</div>
            <h3>{step.title}</h3>
            <p>{step.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section photograph-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What We Photograph</h2>
        <p class="serif">Complete coverage of your property</p>
      </div>
      <div class="photograph-grid">
        {whatWePhotograph.map(item => (
          <div class="photograph-card">
            <h3>{item.title}</h3>
            <p>{item.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section tips-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Photography Tips for Higher Bookings</h2>
        <p class="serif">Prepare your space for the best results</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tips-grid">
        {tips.map((tip) => (
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>{tip.title}</h3>
            <p>{tip.content}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Photography FAQs</h2>
        <p class="serif">Common questions about our photo services</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        {faqs.map(faq => (
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>{faq.q}</h3>
            <p>{faq.a}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section related-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Related Services</h2>
        <p class="serif">Complete your listing optimization</p>
      </div>
      <div class="related-grid">
        {relatedServices.map(service => (
          <a href={service.href} class="related-card">
            <h4>{service.name}</h4>
            <p>{service.description}</p>
            <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to Transform Your Listing?</h2>
        <p>Professional photos pay for themselves within days.</p>
        <a href="tel:647-957-8956" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Call Now: 647-957-8956</a>
        <p class="cta-note">Free consultation • No obligation • Same-day response</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Modern Minimal Design */

  .hero-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  /* Trust Bar - Light & Clean */
  .trust-bar {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .trust-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .trust-item {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .trust-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
